snippet.title: Locks - Official Release Window Trailer | Women-Led Games x TGA 2024
snippet.description: Dive into the surreal world of Locks in this trailer for the upcoming horror puzzle-platformer game set in a puppet show. Locks features a new type of puzzle and a fresh way to scare you. Are you a spectator, participant, or victim? Locks will be available in Q1 2025 on Steam.
